                                    <th class="text-center p-3 font-black uppercase text-xs">Protocolo Necesario</th>
                                    <th class="text-center p-3 font-black uppercase text-xs">Tipo de Cable</th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody>
                                <tr class="border-t border-slate-200"><td class="p-3 font-bold text-sm">iPhone 15/16</td><td class="p-3 text-center">~27W</td><td class="p-3 text-center">PD 3.0 + PPS</td><td class="p-3 text-center">Cualquier USB-C</td></tr>
                                <tr class="border-t border-slate-200"><td class="p-3 font-bold text-sm">Samsung Galaxy S25</td><td class="p-3 text-center">45W</td><td class="p-3 text-center">PD 3.0 + PPS</td><td class="p-3 text-center">E-marker 5A</td></tr>
                                <tr class="border-t border-slate-200"><td class="p-3 font-bold text-sm">MacBook Air M4</td><td class="p-3 text-center">30-45W</td><td class="p-3 text-center">PD 3.0</td><td class="p-3 text-center">Cualquier USB-C</td></tr>
                                <tr class="border-t border-slate-200"><td class="p-3 font-bold text-sm">MacBook Pro 14"</td><td class="p-3 text-center">67-96W</td><td class="p-3 text-center">PD 3.0 SPR</td><td class="p-3 text-center">E-marker 5A</td></tr>
                                <tr class="border-t border-slate-200"><td class="p-3 font-bold text-sm">MacBook Pro 16"</td><td class="p-3 text-center">140W</td><td class="p-3 text-center text-brandBlue font-bold">PD 3.1 EPR</td><td class="p-3 text-center text-brandBlue font-bold">Certificado EPR</td></tr>
                                <tr class="border-t border-slate-200"><td class="p-3 font-bold text-sm">Dell XPS / ThinkPad</td><td class="p-3 text-center">65-100W</td><td class="p-3 text-center">PD 3.0 SPR</td><td class="p-3 text-center">E-marker 5A</td></tr>
                                <tr><td class="p-3 font-bold text-sm">Portátil gaming (RTX 5070+)</td><td class="p-3 text-center">140-240W</td><td class="p-3 text-center text-brandBlue font-bold">PD 3.1 EPR</td><td class="p-3 text-center text-brandBlue font-bold">Certificado EPR</td></tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mt-4"><strong>En resumen:</strong> Para la mayoría de personas en 2026, PD 3.0 con un cable de 5A es todo lo que necesitas. PD 3.1 EPR solo importa si tienes un MacBook Pro 16" o un portátil gaming que cargue a más de 100W por USB-C. No pagues por capacidad de 240W que no usarás — pero sí compra un cargador que admita PPS para una carga rápida óptima de smartphones.</p>
                    </div>
